name: SnowSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open snow sounds”
”Alexa ask snow sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: snow sounds
des: Brrrr! Let the calming sound of a snowstorm outside lull you to sleep. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Snow Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
